data.description: Beautiful 5 bedroom 3 bath home. Features Laminate wood floors downstairs. One Bedroom or study down. Huge Master with his and her closets and 4 beds up gameroom too. Large workshop or storage building in backyard. Recent roof, fence, whole house painting and carpet. Ample storage and closet space. Large bedrooms. Stainless steel dishwasher and fridge.  Solar screens throughout. Oversized lot. Won't last long.
